{
  "texts": [
    "\"we had planned on having three distinct engineering squads… through ChatGPT, we can get our roadmap done with one less squad… that [is] huge\" These savings and benefits would be difficult and costly to achieve if the Gen AI tool required a custom data set.",
    "However, the CEO also identified some trade-offs in the decision to adopt the general LLM, including privacy concerns.",
    "This informant admitted that the company was unsure if everything uploaded onto ChatGPT would remain private or be used as input in responding to others' prompts.",
    "As a safeguard against privacy breaches, the technology teams uploaded only a subsection of code onto ChatGPT, not the firm's full code library.",
    "Executives asserted that even if recent ChatGPT promise of privacy, this concern is likely to persist."
  ]
}